WEBVTT

00:00:03.470 --> 00:00:08.154
(Astral)
Something strange and incredible
is happening in the human world.

00:00:08.154 --> 00:00:11.991
I sensed it when the 107th
Number appeared.

00:00:12.158 --> 00:00:16.196
And when I saw the two
Galaxy-Eyes facing each other,

00:00:16.196 --> 00:00:18.431
I was sure of it.

00:00:18.431 --> 00:00:21.134
As the battle unfolded, my
suspicion grew even stronger

00:00:21.134 --> 00:00:24.404
when our opponent Mizar revealed
his true Barian form.

00:00:24.904 --> 00:00:28.775
I am afraid this can
only mean one thing...

00:00:28.775 --> 00:00:31.744
the Barians are
about to make a critical move!

00:00:31.744 --> 00:00:35.815
I can sense that Yuma is just as
anxious and confused as I am.

00:00:36.916 --> 00:00:41.020
The Sphere Field used against
us is extremely powerful.

00:00:41.020 --> 00:00:44.857
I believe it affects
not just the body,

00:00:44.857 --> 00:00:47.093
but the mind and
spirit as well.

00:00:47.093 --> 00:00:49.729
The damage it inflicted
was so intense,

00:00:49.729 --> 00:00:52.065
I needed to retreat inside
the Golden Key to recover.

00:00:52.432 --> 00:00:55.969
Yuma is worried about me;

00:00:55.969 --> 00:00:57.437
I can sense that his confidence
has been shaken.

00:00:57.670 --> 00:01:00.440
This is a dangerous moment.

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:02.809
Our foes are growing stronger.

00:01:02.809 --> 00:01:04.844
Yuma wants to protect me,
but if he is too cautious,

00:01:04.844 --> 00:01:08.014
he will not have the ability
to defeat the Barians.

00:01:12.952 --> 00:01:16.322
(Yuma) Astral!

00:01:16.322 --> 00:01:17.423
You depend on me
and I let you down.

00:01:17.657 --> 00:01:20.293
I'm sorry.

00:01:20.293 --> 00:01:22.061
From now on, I promise
I'll be more careful.

