♪ Still together as one 'cause
divided we're none ♪

00:01:37.944 --> 00:01:40.813
♪ Ready to go
we feel the flow ♪

00:01:40.813 --> 00:01:43.416
♪ So don't stand in our way
you know we ain't afraid ♪

00:01:43.416 --> 00:01:46.152
♪ This is our time
we're in control ♪

00:01:46.152 --> 00:01:48.688
♪ If I trip up today
you'll just wipe it away ♪

00:01:48.688 --> 00:01:51.424
♪ All of my fears
are gone erased ♪

00:01:51.424 --> 00:01:54.027
♪ Let us tear down the walls
till the final night falls ♪

00:01:54.027 --> 00:01:56.829
♪ The bonds of our
souls can't be replaced ♪

00:01:56.829 --> 00:01:59.432
♪ Let us fight together
regretting never ♪

00:01:59.666 --> 00:02:02.835
♪ Our dreams will be ♪

00:02:02.835 --> 00:02:04.937
♪ Halfway to forever our
light comes shining through ♪

00:02:06.005 --> 00:02:10.043
♪ Reach down deep beat defeat
do all that we can do ♪

00:02:11.377 --> 00:02:15.381
♪ Halfway to forever
we've got nothing to lose ♪

00:02:16.449 --> 00:02:20.653
♪ Keep breathing believing
halfway to forever ♪ ♪

00:02:32.432 --> 00:02:36.135
I knew you were irresponsible,

00:02:36.135 --> 00:02:38.204
but even I never thought you
could be so reckless

00:02:38.204 --> 00:02:40.907
that you landed
yourself in the hospital.

00:02:40.907 --> 00:02:43.109
And not just you,
but your friend too.

00:02:43.109 --> 00:02:46.446
What's his name again,
uh, Reginald?

00:02:46.446 --> 00:02:49.148
You could've been badly hurt!

00:02:49.148 --> 00:02:51.351
The doctor says neither of you
has any serious injuries,

00:02:51.351 --> 00:02:54.153
so you can
count yourselves lucky.

00:02:54.153 --> 00:02:56.422
Still, that doesn't excuse
your foolish behavior.

00:02:56.422 --> 00:02:59.359
Excuse me, my brother
is trying to rest,

00:02:59.359 --> 00:03:02.795
so I'd appreciate it if you
could keep it down in here.

00:03:02.795 --> 00:03:06.165
Of course, sorry.

00:03:06.165 --> 00:03:08.201
Yuma, I have to go to work, so
stay in bed and out of trouble.

00:03:08.201 --> 00:03:11.437
Got that?
All right.

00:03:11.437 --> 00:03:15.274
Yuma, your sister
could strike fear

00:03:15.274 --> 00:03:17.076
into the heart of
a grizzly bear.

00:03:17.076 --> 00:03:19.045
You two certainly are
different from each other.

00:03:19.045 --> 00:03:21.948
Yeah, she's a lot more
serious than you are.

00:03:21.948 --> 00:03:24.917
Taller too!

00:03:24.917 --> 00:03:26.953
Hey guys, keep it down
or we're gonna wake up Shark!

00:03:29.055 --> 00:03:32.325
I forgot!

00:03:32.325 --> 00:03:33.826
That's okay.

00:03:33.826 --> 00:03:35.228
Shark's awake.

00:03:35.228 --> 00:03:36.429
(all) Huh?

00:03:36.429 --> 00:03:38.197
I said that he was resting,
not sleeping.

00:03:38.197 --> 00:03:41.100
I did it because
I thought it might help

00:03:41.100 --> 00:03:42.435
calm Yuma's sister down,
and it sure seemed to work.

00:03:42.668 --> 00:03:45.938
Rio, close that curtain.

00:03:45.938 --> 00:03:48.040
Huh? But why?

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:49.876
Because with
the curtain closed,

00:03:49.876 --> 00:03:51.878
it's easier to forget that
I'm rooming with a wimp.

00:03:56.015 --> 00:03:59.152
Ugh.

00:04:00.887 --> 00:04:04.424
What is wrong with him?

00:04:14.934 --> 00:04:18.237
You look weak.

00:04:18.237 --> 00:04:19.972
Have I worn you down?

00:04:19.972 --> 00:04:21.808
If you need a break, I'd be
happy to give it to you!

00:04:21.808 --> 00:04:25.411
Attack with Tachyon
Spiral of Destruction!

00:04:33.386 --> 00:04:36.722
It was a dream.

00:04:36.722 --> 00:04:38.424
It's okay.

00:04:38.424 --> 00:04:39.826
Calm down.

00:04:39.826 --> 00:04:41.894
You're letting your fear
take complete control of you,

00:04:41.894 --> 00:04:44.197
even in your sleep!

00:04:44.197 --> 00:04:45.865
I can't take anymore!
Snap out of it already!

00:04:45.865 --> 00:04:49.168
I mean it, Yuma.

00:04:49.168 --> 00:04:50.736
Quiet down!

00:04:50.736 --> 00:04:52.672
Do you loudmouths have any idea
what time it is?!

00:04:55.842 --> 00:04:59.445
Don't you understand, Kite?

00:04:59.445 --> 00:05:01.414
Your friend's in the hospital.

00:05:01.414 --> 00:05:02.982
You should go visit him.

00:05:03.416 --> 00:05:04.183
All right.

00:05:06.652 --> 00:05:07.887
You may not think this is
important, but I do.

00:05:07.887 --> 00:05:10.723
Wait, Hart.

00:05:10.723 --> 00:05:12.925
Where are you going?

00:05:12.925 --> 00:05:14.393
I'm going to see Yuma,
of course.

00:05:14.393 --> 00:05:16.829
Master K-K-Kite!

00:05:16.829 --> 00:05:18.130
I ch-checked the hospital's
visiting hours.

00:05:18.130 --> 00:05:20.032
You should
leave s-s-soon.

00:05:20.032 --> 00:05:21.834
But I hope you're not expecting
me to pop-pop-pop in on that

00:05:21.834 --> 00:05:24.303
pitiful little pest!

00:05:24.303 --> 00:05:26.439
I knew you'd go, Kite!

00:05:28.174 --> 00:05:31.811
I'm glad Yuma's out
getting a checkup.

00:05:31.811 --> 00:05:34.046
At least he won't be able
to annoy me for a while.

00:05:45.791 --> 00:05:49.262
Hey, what's this about?

00:05:49.262 --> 00:05:51.130
(Shark)
"Yuma, I've taken
your little necklace.

00:05:51.130 --> 00:05:54.066
If you want it back, then you'll
have to duel me for it.

00:05:54.066 --> 00:05:56.869
I'll be waiting
for you on the roof."

00:06:06.212 --> 00:06:09.448
You showed up...
Good.

00:06:09.682 --> 00:06:11.317
What's the point
of doing this, Shark?

00:06:11.317 --> 00:06:13.419
Why did you take my Golden Key?

00:06:13.653 --> 00:06:15.421
That's not important, Yuma.

00:06:15.421 --> 00:06:17.423
All that matters now
is that I have it,

00:06:17.423 --> 00:06:19.825
and you're never going to
get it back unless you beat me.

00:06:20.826 --> 00:06:24.063
Let's go!

00:06:26.032 --> 00:06:29.869
You better be at
the top of your game, Yuma.

00:06:32.171 --> 00:06:35.441
'Cause I can promise you
that in this duel,

00:06:35.441 --> 00:06:37.910
I won't hold back!

00:06:39.779 --> 00:06:43.883
(computer voice)
Augmented Reality
Vision Link established.

00:06:44.417 --> 00:06:46.385
(both) Let's duel!

00:06:50.723 --> 00:06:53.926
Yuma...

00:06:55.428 --> 00:06:58.798
It's my move!

00:06:58.798 --> 00:07:01.233
I'm putting a monster card
facedown in defense mode.

00:07:02.301 --> 00:07:04.337
(Yuma)
I don't wanna
take any chances.

00:07:06.172 --> 00:07:07.940
It's a good thing I have
Gogogo Golem on the field

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:10.109
to protect me.

00:07:10.109 --> 00:07:11.444
You can take it
from here, Shark.

00:07:11.444 --> 00:07:13.713
That's it?
Only one lousy move?

00:07:13.713 --> 00:07:15.948
You're not trying to win;
you're just scared of losing!

00:07:15.948 --> 00:07:19.385
There's nothing wrong with
playing it safe, Shark.

00:07:19.385 --> 00:07:23.122
I can't believe
how pathetic you've become.

00:07:23.122 --> 00:07:26.292
Here!

00:07:31.964 --> 00:07:35.935
Without Astral to help you,
you're no threat at all,

00:07:35.935 --> 00:07:39.038
so team up with him
if you have to.

00:07:39.038 --> 00:07:41.440
It's my move.

00:07:42.441 --> 00:07:43.075
What's wrong?

00:07:45.911 --> 00:07:47.013
Astral isn't coming
to save you?

00:07:47.013 --> 00:07:49.448
Looks like he's finally
realized what a loser you are!

00:07:52.852 --> 00:07:56.722
First, I'll activate my
spell card Fish Spawn!

00:08:00.026 --> 00:08:03.295
If I give up
a thousand life points,

00:08:03.295 --> 00:08:05.231
this spell lets me summon
two Fish Spawn Tokens.

00:08:06.432 --> 00:08:08.401
But I'm going to tribute
both of them immediately

00:08:10.436 --> 00:08:12.972
because then I can summon a
Level Nine monster... Big Whale!

00:08:13.973 --> 00:08:18.010
When it surfaces, any face-down
monsters in defense mode

00:08:18.711 --> 00:08:22.081
are blown face-up.

00:08:22.081 --> 00:08:23.949
Unlike your meek strategy,

00:08:23.949 --> 00:08:25.718
I'm going big and bold, Yuma!

00:08:25.851 --> 00:08:28.421
There's more, 'cause Big Whale's
special ability will let me

00:08:29.955 --> 00:08:32.992
summon one Water Attribute
monster from my hand

00:08:32.992 --> 00:08:36.295
if it's Level Four or less!

00:08:36.295 --> 00:08:38.264
Burst onto the scene,
Drill Barnacle!

00:08:40.966 --> 00:08:44.437
Next I'll activate
my Tri-Slice spell!

00:08:45.271 --> 00:08:47.306
