of Water Attribute monsters

00:08:51.444 --> 00:08:54.780
just as long as their Levels
are a third of Big Whale's!

00:08:54.780 --> 00:08:58.384
I hope you like Starfish
'cause here come three of 'em!

00:09:01.987 --> 00:09:05.257
What are you up to?

00:09:05.257 --> 00:09:06.959
You're about
to find out, loser!

00:09:06.959 --> 00:09:09.228
I overlay two Level
Three Starfish

00:09:09.228 --> 00:09:12.898
and I'll use them both
to build the Overlay Network!

00:09:12.898 --> 00:09:15.868
See where this is going?

00:09:16.035 --> 00:09:17.703
I Xyz Summon!

00:09:19.338 --> 00:09:21.140
Submersible Carrier Aero Shark!

00:09:21.140 --> 00:09:24.343
And next up, I'm overlaying
Drill Barnacle

00:09:24.343 --> 00:09:27.346
and my last Starfish!

00:09:27.346 --> 00:09:29.381
Not another Xyz Summon?

00:09:29.381 --> 00:09:31.784
That's right, Yuma.

00:09:31.784 --> 00:09:34.053
I'm Xyz Summoning the champion
of darkness and devastation,

00:09:34.854 --> 00:09:38.224
Black Ray Lancer!

00:09:38.224 --> 00:09:40.826
Great... One Xyz monster's
bad enough,

00:09:40.826 --> 00:09:43.129
but now I have to
go up against two of 'em!

00:09:43.129 --> 00:09:46.365
You got that right!

00:09:46.365 --> 00:09:48.167
I activate Aero Shark's
special ability.

00:09:48.167 --> 00:09:51.437
So all I have to do is use an
Overlay Unit and you'll take

00:09:51.670 --> 00:09:54.940
400 points of damage
for each card in my hand.

00:09:54.940 --> 00:09:58.277
I happen to have two.

00:09:58.277 --> 00:10:00.346
Go Torpedo Takedown!

00:10:06.986 --> 00:10:10.790
Now I activate Black Ray
Lancer's ability!

00:10:10.790 --> 00:10:14.293
By using one Overlay Unit,
your Golem's special abilities

00:10:14.293 --> 00:10:17.429
are negated this turn!

00:10:17.429 --> 00:10:19.765
Paralyzing Lance!

00:10:21.801 --> 00:10:24.904
This is what
"playing it safe" gets you.

00:10:25.437 --> 00:10:27.706
Quick, Aero Shark!

00:10:29.008 --> 00:10:30.876
Destroy that Golem
with Devouring Dive!

00:10:34.446 --> 00:10:38.417
Nothing can protect you
if I attack now, Yuma!

00:10:38.417 --> 00:10:41.921
Black Ray Lancer,
attack Yuma directly!

00:10:42.388 --> 00:10:45.858
Shimmering Spear Slash!

00:10:49.395 --> 00:10:53.232
You've taken enough punishment
for one turn.

00:10:53.232 --> 00:10:56.001
It's your move.

00:10:56.435 --> 00:10:57.803
Come on, get up on your feet.

00:11:00.105 --> 00:11:02.041
Or is this duel
too much for you!?

00:11:02.041 --> 00:11:04.944
No, it's not!

00:11:06.345 --> 00:11:09.381
(Yuma)
I have to take on
two Xyz monsters.

00:11:09.381 --> 00:11:11.717
But since my only monster
was destroyed,

00:11:11.717 --> 00:11:13.853
I'm starting from scratch.

00:11:13.853 --> 00:11:16.856
I'll go big this time!

00:11:16.856 --> 00:11:18.891
I'm summoning Gogogo Giant
in attack mode!

00:11:24.430 --> 00:11:28.434
All right, you're
starting to put up a fight.

00:11:28.434 --> 00:11:32.438
(Yuma)
Gogogo Giant has
2000 attack points.

00:11:32.438 --> 00:11:35.741
It's powerful enough to take
down Aero Shark,

00:11:35.741 --> 00:11:38.377
but it's definitely not strong
enough to beat

00:11:38.377 --> 00:11:40.246
Black Ray Lancer.

00:11:40.246 --> 00:11:42.448
In that case...

00:11:42.448 --> 00:11:44.383
I'd better use
its special ability!

00:11:44.383 --> 00:11:48.087
Since I summoned Gogogo Giant,
I can also summon Gogogo Golem

00:11:48.087 --> 00:11:51.790
from my graveyard
in defense mode.

00:11:51.790 --> 00:11:54.226
Once that ability's used,

00:11:54.226 --> 00:11:55.761
I have to switch Gogogo Giant
into defense mode, too.

00:11:55.761 --> 00:11:59.365
I'll follow that up by
activating my spell card

00:11:59.365 --> 00:12:01.934
Gogogo Talisman!

00:12:01.934 --> 00:12:04.069
It'll keep my Gogogo monsters
out of danger.

00:12:04.069 --> 00:12:06.972
It protects them from being
destroyed once per battle.

00:12:06.972 --> 00:12:09.875
And for extra safety,
whenever I have two or more

00:12:09.875 --> 00:12:12.344
Gogogo monsters, effects
can't damage me either!

00:12:12.344 --> 00:12:15.447
I can't deal any damage
this turn...

00:12:15.447 --> 00:12:18.183
but at least
I'll be well-shielded from

00:12:18.183 --> 00:12:19.985
your Aero Shark's torpedoes!

00:12:19.985 --> 00:12:22.321
With that, I'll end my turn.

00:12:22.321 --> 00:12:24.390
Those moves won't save you!

00:12:24.390 --> 00:12:26.091
Nothing will, because you're
a miserable coward!

00:12:26.091 --> 00:12:29.428
You'll never win another duel,

00:12:29.428 --> 00:12:31.163
'cause you're letting
your fears rule you!

00:12:31.430 --> 00:12:35.134
Those moves won't save you!

00:12:35.134 --> 00:12:37.002
Nothing will because you're
a miserable coward!

00:12:37.002 --> 00:12:40.172
You'll never win another duel,

00:12:40.172 --> 00:12:41.874
'cause you're
letting your fears rule you!

00:12:43.876 --> 00:12:47.446
(Astral)
Yuma, you must understand.

00:12:47.446 --> 00:12:50.082
The enemies we are about to face
are more powerful than any

00:12:50.082 --> 00:12:52.952
we have known before.

00:12:52.952 --> 00:12:54.420
You must be ready for the
challenge, but the strength you

00:12:54.420 --> 00:12:56.922
need for what lies ahead can
only be found within you.

00:13:00.426 --> 00:13:03.963
Time to crush you!

00:13:03.963 --> 00:13:05.998
I draw!

00:13:05.998 --> 00:13:07.399
I'll start this turn by
summoning Panther Shark!

00:13:07.433 --> 00:13:11.437
When you have at least two
monsters on the field,

00:13:11.437 --> 00:13:13.939
I can summon this card
without having to tribute

00:13:13.939 --> 00:13:16.008
another monster!

00:13:16.008 --> 00:13:18.143
Yeah, let it roar,
Panther Shark!

00:13:18.444 --> 00:13:22.881
In fact, this whole field is
about to be shark-infested,

00:13:22.881 --> 00:13:26.418
because once I
summon Panther Shark,

00:13:26.418 --> 00:13:28.420
I can also summon Eagle
Shark from my hand.

00:13:29.888 --> 00:13:33.892
I overlay my Level Five
Panther Shark and Eagle Shark

00:13:33.892 --> 00:13:37.296
in order to build the Overlay
Network and Xyz Summon.

00:13:42.735 --> 00:13:46.739
Now I can bring forth
the most fearsome stronghold

00:13:46.739 --> 00:13:49.441
in the seas...
Shark Fortress!

00:13:58.417 --> 00:14:02.421
That gives him three Xyz
monsters on his field!

00:14:02.421 --> 00:14:05.424
And it's gonna get worse, Yuma!

00:14:05.424 --> 00:14:07.426
Because I'm bulking up
Black Ray Lancer

00:14:07.659 --> 00:14:10.195
with the equip spell Sharkify!

00:14:12.765 --> 00:14:16.402
When it's equipped
with this card,

00:14:16.402 --> 00:14:18.070
my Lancer
becomes a Shark monster.

00:14:18.070 --> 00:14:20.439
Plus it gets stronger by
400 attack points!

00:14:20.439 --> 00:14:23.776
Next, I'm going to use an
Overlay Unit to activate

00:14:23.776 --> 00:14:26.178
Black Shark Lancer's
special ability!

00:14:26.178 --> 00:14:29.448
Which means it can now negate
your GOLEM's abilities!

00:14:32.017 --> 00:14:34.353
Coward, you deserve everything
that's about to happen to you!

00:14:36.889 --> 00:14:40.225
Now Aero Shark,

00:14:40.225 --> 00:14:41.827
dive at Gogogo Giant
and eliminate it!

00:14:42.094 --> 00:14:45.898
I activate my Gogogo
Talisman's effect.

00:14:45.898 --> 00:14:49.268
Once per turn, this spell can
stop a monster from being

00:14:49.268 --> 00:14:51.870
destroyed in battle!

00:14:51.870 --> 00:14:53.439
So what!?
I'll just attack again!

00:14:53.439 --> 00:14:56.408
Black Shark Lancer,
bring down that Giant!

00:15:01.447 --> 00:15:05.050
But I'm not finished yet!

00:15:05.050 --> 00:15:07.086
Shark Fortress, blast
Gogogo Golem into dust!

00:15:09.421 --> 00:15:11.223
My Talisman will negate
that Shark!

00:15:19.731 --> 00:15:23.368
I survived all three attacks.

00:15:23.368 --> 00:15:25.437
I'm not done!

00:15:25.437 --> 00:15:27.439
Didn't I say
I wouldn't hold back!?

00:15:27.439 --> 00:15:29.842
I set all this up as
part of my strategy.

00:15:29.842 --> 00:15:32.444
By using an Overlay Unit,
Shark Fortress' special ability

00:15:32.444 --> 00:15:35.447
gives one of my other Shark
monsters an extra attack.

00:15:35.681 --> 00:15:38.817
So I'm coming after you
with Aero Shark!

00:15:38.817 --> 00:15:41.420
Shark Fortress, arm Aero Shark

00:15:41.420 --> 00:15:43.422
with one of your mighty
Mayhem Missiles!

00:15:44.256 --> 00:15:46.325
Your target
will be Gogogo Golem!

00:15:55.701 --> 00:15:59.037
Launch missile!

00:16:03.442 --> 00:16:07.713
And since you don't have any
Gogogo monsters on your field,

00:16:07.713 --> 00:16:10.749
you can say goodbye
to your Talisman!

00:16:10.749 --> 00:16:13.152
You're defenseless now!

00:16:13.152 --> 00:16:14.786
Once again, I activate my
Fortress' special ability.

00:16:14.786 --> 00:16:18.390
I'll use an Overlay Unit to
give one of my Shark monsters

00:16:18.390 --> 00:16:21.426
an additional attack.

00:16:21.426 --> 00:16:23.428
You're up this time,
Black Shark Lancer.

00:16:23.662 --> 00:16:26.365
Arm yourself!

00:16:30.802 --> 00:16:34.773
Black Shark Lancer, prepare
to attack Yuma directly!

00:16:36.441 --> 00:16:38.243
Fire on my command!

00:16:40.946 --> 00:16:44.883
Black Shark Lancer, prepare
to attack Yuma directly!

00:16:46.652 --> 00:16:48.420
Fire on my command!

00:16:50.055 --> 00:16:52.324
(Yuma)
This is like having the same
bad dream over and over.

00:16:53.959 --> 00:16:57.095
I'm gonna lose the duel
and there's nothing I can do.

00:16:57.095 --> 00:17:00.732
It's just like my battle
with Mizar.

00:17:00.732 --> 00:17:02.901
I couldn't protect Astral then

00:17:02.901 --> 00:17:04.770
and now I can't even
protect myself!

00:17:04.770 --> 00:17:07.973
No matter how hard I try,
I can't keep from losing.

00:17:09.875 --> 00:17:11.977
Maybe Shark is right; I have
been playing it too safe.

00:17:13.946 --> 00:17:17.683
All this time I've been so
scared of losing,

00:17:17.683 --> 00:17:19.952
that I've stopped
really trying to win.

00:17:22.421 --> 00:17:25.924
I have to stop hiding
behind my cards.

00:17:25.924 --> 00:17:28.327
I wanna try to
high-five the sky again,

00:17:28.327 --> 00:17:30.429
together with Astral!

00:17:30.429 --> 00:17:32.097
(Astral)
That is exactly
what I have been

00:17:33.999 --> 00:17:35.867
waiting to hear you say, Yuma.

00:17:35.867 --> 00:17:38.403
I thought I'd
never see you again.

00:17:38.403 --> 00:17:41.240
We are a team, Yuma, but
we cannot be effective

00:17:41.240 --> 00:17:43.442
unless we duel without fear.

00:17:43.442 --> 00:17:45.444
If we battle boldly, we truly
can high-five the sky!

00:17:45.677 --> 00:17:49.147
Now summon Gagaga Gardna!

00:17:49.147 --> 00:17:52.417
Yeah, he's right.

00:17:52.417 --> 00:17:53.986
I summon Gagaga Gardna
from my hand!

00:17:55.354 --> 00:17:58.423
It's lucky you're
attacking me directly, Shark,

00:17:58.423 --> 00:18:01.093
'cause that lets me summon
Gardna in attack mode!

00:18:01.093 --> 00:18:04.429
And by discarding
one card from my hand,

00:18:04.429 --> 00:18:06.431
this monster can't be
destroyed in battle!

00:18:10.435 --> 00:18:14.239
Your Gardna won't be destroyed,

00:18:14.239 --> 00:18:15.974
but you'll still take
major damage, Yuma!

00:18:19.978 --> 00:18:23.448
And with that, I end my turn.

00:18:23.448 --> 00:18:26.251
You can still win.
Yeah.

00:18:26.251 --> 00:18:28.854
I know my chances
don't look too good,

00:18:28.854 --> 00:18:31.123
but when we're working
as a team,

00:18:31.123 --> 00:18:33.258
nothing can ever stop us.

00:18:33.258 --> 00:18:36.428
Exactly.

00:18:36.995 --> 00:18:37.663
Then let's go!

00:18:40.332 --> 00:18:43.068
Yes!

00:18:43.068 --> 00:18:44.202
You now have everything
you need to win.

00:18:44.202 --> 00:18:46.438
Right.

00:18:46.438 --> 00:18:48.440
I'm summoning Ganbara Knight!

00:18:52.244 --> 00:18:56.281
Next up, I'm overlaying
my Level Four Gagaga Gardna

00:18:56.281 --> 00:18:59.718
and Ganbara Knight!

00:18:59.718 --> 00:19:02.254
With these two monsters
I build the Overlay Network!

00:19:02.254 --> 00:19:05.691
I Xyz Summon Heroic
Champion... Excalibur!

00:19:13.799 --> 00:19:17.202
That's more like it!

00:19:17.202 --> 00:19:18.737
I'll follow that up
by equipping

00:19:18.737 --> 00:19:20.872
Magnum Shield on Excalibur!

00:19:20.872 --> 00:19:23.675
Thanks to this shield,
Excalibur's defense points

00:19:23.675 --> 00:19:26.211
are added to its attack points.

00:19:33.752 --> 00:19:37.122
Only 4,000 points?

00:19:37.122 --> 00:19:38.790
Please.

00:19:38.790 --> 00:19:39.858
That's clearly not
enough to win this duel.

00:19:39.858 --> 00:19:42.260
Okay Excalibur, use your
special ability!

00:19:43.762 --> 00:19:45.931
When it uses all
its Overlay Units,

00:19:47.432 --> 00:19:49.935
Excalibur doubles its
attack points during battle!

00:19:50.369 --> 00:19:53.705
Do it now, Yuma!

00:19:53.705 --> 00:19:55.907
Watch out, 'cause I'm
feelin' the flow!

00:19:55.907 --> 00:19:59.277
Excalibur, demolish
that Shark Fortress!

00:19:59.277 --> 00:20:02.748
Shock Sword Slash!

00:20:18.997 --> 00:20:22.434
Mission accomplished!

00:20:31.042 --> 00:20:34.379
Oh no, Shark!

00:20:34.379 --> 00:20:36.415
Are you okay?

00:20:36.415 --> 00:20:38.383
I'm fine.

00:20:38.383 --> 00:20:39.818
Thank you.

00:20:39.818 --> 00:20:41.019
Your challenge was exactly
what Yuma needed.

00:20:41.019 --> 00:20:44.156
You helped him to
regain his fighting spirit.

00:20:44.156 --> 00:20:46.758
I am grateful.

00:20:46.758 --> 00:20:48.059
Hey, don't thank me.

00:20:48.059 --> 00:20:49.294
I only challenged Yuma
'cause he annoyed me.

00:20:49.294 --> 00:20:51.863
And yet, you clearly tried to
help Yuma overcome his fear.

00:20:52.798 --> 00:20:56.234
No, that's ridiculous!

00:20:56.234 --> 00:20:59.438
Shark, thank you.

00:20:59.438 --> 00:21:01.239
You're a true friend.

00:21:01.239 --> 00:21:03.375
Look, don't get all
emotional or else.

00:21:03.375 --> 00:21:06.311
You've annoyed me
enough for one day.
But I...

00:21:06.311 --> 00:21:08.880
(Astral) Observation Number 22:

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:11.049
Humans express their friendship
in many different ways.

00:21:11.283 --> 00:21:15.253
Some do it quite loudly,
while others speak volumes

00:21:15.253 --> 00:21:18.423
with their silence.

00:21:18.423 --> 00:21:19.858
(Shark)
...totally
make that happen!

00:21:19.858 --> 00:21:21.026
(Yuma)
Aw, come on, Shark,
don't be like that.

00:21:21.026 --> 00:21:22.861
Come here, let's hug it out.

00:21:22.861 --> 00:21:24.763
Get away from me.

00:21:24.763 --> 00:21:25.897
I mean it, you're
gonna ruin my threads!

00:21:25.897 --> 00:21:27.432
I prefer the latter.

00:21:27.666 --> 00:21:30.068
Ruin your threads,
you can't ruin Polyester.

00:21:30.068 --> 00:21:32.437
Did you say Polyester?

